text: The Fifth Estate is a 2013 drama-thriller movie based on the real life events of WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange. It stars Benedict Cumberbatch, Laura Linney, and Stanley Tucci. It was released on October 18, 2013 to negative reviews. Category:2013 movies Category:American drama movies Category:American thriller movies Category:DreamWorks Pictures movies
